<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-7888] HL7Decoder leaks memory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-7888</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Under constant load (i.e. Mina session never idles out), the HL7Decoder leaks memory. In fact, all received messages are appended to Mina&apos;s IOBuffer, which leads to OOME after some time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
